===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The {{vern|common weasel}}, {{vern|little weasel}}, or simply [[weasel]] (''[[Mustela nivalis]]''), the [[small]]est [[member]] of the [[weasel]] [[genus]] ''[[Mustela]]'', [[native#Adjective|native]] to [[Eurasia]], [[North America]], and [[North Africa]].

